\{f_{n}\}\subseteq C_{C}(X)
f_{n}\longrightarrow f\in C(X)
\epsilon>0
\exists n\in \mathbb{N}
\|f_{n}-f\|_{u}<\epsilon
\vert f(x) \vert<\epsilon
